# Phase 6 Keyboard Shortcuts Implementation Guide
#
# This patch file documents the changes needed to implement keyboard shortcuts
# for Pro Mode in MapView.jsx
#
# The following shortcuts are implemented:
# | Key | Action |
# |-----|--------|
# | ? | Show keyboard shortcut help overlay |
# | F | Toggle filter menu |
# | D | Toggle FPS counter (debug) |
# | M | Toggle MSAW (Minimum Safe Altitude Warning) |
# | W | Toggle watch list panel |
# | N | Add selected aircraft to watch list |
# | J | Toggle J-rings |
# | Escape | Also closes help overlay |
#
# Components created:
# - /web/src/components/map/components/KeyboardShortcutHelp.jsx
# - CSS added to /web/src/styles/pro-mode.css
#
# Existing hooks that can be used:
# - /web/src/hooks/useWatchList.js
# - /web/src/hooks/useMSAW.js
# - /web/src/components/map/components/WatchListPanel.jsx
#
# Changes needed in keyboard shortcuts switch statement:
# 1. Add case '?' for help overlay
# 2. Change case 'f' from FPS to filter menu
# 3. Add case 'd' for FPS counter
# 4. Change case 'm' from reduced motion to MSAW
# 5. Add case 'w' for watch list panel
# 6. Add case 'n' for adding to watch list
# 7. Add case 'j' for J-rings
# 8. Modify escape to also close help overlay
# 9. Update dependency array to include selectedAircraft
# 10. Add KeyboardShortcutHelp component render
